        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>Small Business Size Standard Manufacturing Clarification Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill extends the period of time (from one year to five years) for which a manufacturing concern's average employment is to be considered for a determination of whether the manufacturer is a small business.</p>]]></text>
